caller_intent: The caller requested a budget/quote for obtaining insurance and mentioned they currently do not have any policy.
resolution_steps: Agent acknowledged the caller's request for a budget/quote.
Agent informed the caller they would be transferred to a Spanish-speaking agent.
Agent instructed the caller to leave a voicemail if the Spanish-speaking agent was unavailable.
summary: A caller requested a budget for insurance and mentioned having no existing policy. The agent transferred the call to a Spanish-speaking agent and instructed the caller to leave a voicemail if unavailable. The call was not resolved during this interaction.
